name: Guido Corleone - FUCKAGASFEE
description: The First Hip Hop Music Video NFT on hic et nunc! One tree will be planted with each piece purchased! Guido Corleone (Luminaries/Truth & Love) AKA Chris Devcich's Genesis piece with an ode to sustainable ways of creating art in the NFT space, the frustration us artists have felt in minting and having to pay, or choose not to pay - gas fees. Shout out to finding a way to make art by any means necessary, & use our creative energy to help the living planet we live with. chrisdevcich@gmail.com
